Strictly validate :class:`~icalendar.prop.dt.date.vDate` and :class:`~icalendar.prop.dt.time.vTime` values in their ``from_ical`` methods and reject malformed input, matching the strictness added to :class:`~icalendar.prop.dt.datetime.vDatetime`. Trailing data and ``int()`` quirks (underscores, whitespace, signs) are no longer silently accepted, per :rfc:`5545#section-3.3.4` and :rfc:`5545#section-3.3.12`. @alhudz
